At Texas Star Rentals, we take pride in being your premier destination for top-tier vehicle rentals. With a fleet of over 100+ meticulously maintained vehicles, we offer the perfect ride for every occasion. Our commitment to excellence is reflected in the countless five-star reviews from satisfied customers who have experienced the Texas Star Rentals difference. Whether you're seeking luxury, reliability, or versatility, our diverse selection of vehicles is designed to exceed your expectations. Discover the Lone Star State with confidence and style, courtesy of Texas Star Rentals.

DELIVERY: To enhance your convenience, we provide vehicle delivery to various destinations. Additional parking fees apply for airport locations, ranging from $5 to $10.

Our options include:
- Pick up at our location (No charge)
- Delivery to your address (Delivery fee applies)
- Delivery to the airport (Delivery fee applies)
- Delivery to various hotels in the Metropolitan area (Delivery fee applies)

RE-FUELING: Vehicles are supplied with fuel and should be returned with the same level. If you prefer, we can handle refueling for you at an additional $10 fee plus the gas invoice. Please note the fuel grade, conveniently located on the gas tank cover (premium or regular).

TOLL ROAD CHARGES: Our vehicles come equipped with a Toll Tag for your convenience. You may use tolls during your trip, but expect charges for usage. Upon receiving the toll statement, reimbursement will be requested via the app.

MILEAGE: Mileage is limited 200 per day, and exceeding the allotted miles per trip will result in additional charges at a $0.25 per-mile rate.

WASH/NO PETS: Vehicles should be returned in the same condition as delivered. Excessive dirtiness, determined by our Service Director, will incur a cleaning fee. Additionally, a $150 pet fee will be charged for any evidence of pet hair upon return. Your understanding and adherence to this policy are appreciated.

NO SMOKING: Our cars are smoke and pet-free. Smoking of any kind is strictly prohibited, and a $250 Smoking fee will be applied to your Turo Reservation if smoke smell is detected. We kindly request compliance with this policy.

Hassle-free: Above all, we prioritize your satisfaction! Should you have any questions or require assistance, please feel free to contact us anytime.
Rent out Pearl (Mazda CX-5, 2015) or Jeep (Wrangler Sahara 4 door, 2017) while in the Houston area. All we ask is no beach trips unless owner specifically okays your request.
